data.title: Daniel Strickland
data.content: Thanks @whiteribbonaust for having me at your #whiteribbon breakfast at Canberra Parliament House. Wonderful to hear from an extraordinary survivor @angejay & also words from the Australian Prime Minister @turnbullmalcolm & leader of the opposition @billshortenmp #whiteribbonaust #whiteribbonambassador #canberra now back to #goulburn for me. #missionaustralia #newselfwales
